                                                          <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                                                    <note>According to the colophon, the writing of <ref target="#ms_i1">Text I</ref> and
                                                    <ref target="#ms_i2">Text II</ref> was completed on <date>2 Ṗāgumen 1962 EC</date>
                                                        (= <date>7 September 1969 CE</date>), by <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13233DerarWaldaQirqos">ʾalaqā Dǝrār Walda Qirqos</persName>,
                                                       at <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC7348Legat">Lǝggāt</placeName>. The commissioner was
                                                      <persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13234MehrataWaldaKidan">wayzāro Mǝḥratā Walda Kidān</persName> who paid 220 Ethiopian <foreign xml:lang="gez">Bǝrr</foreign>
                                                      and donated the book to <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2320DabraM">Däbrä Maʿṣo</placeName>.</note>
                                                      <locus target="#89ra"/>
                                                      <hi rend="rubric">ተፈጸመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አመ፡</hi> <date calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1962-13-2" when="1969-08-07">፪ለጳጉሜን፡ በ፲ወ፱፻፷ወ፪ዓመተ፡</date>
                                                       ምሕረት፡ በ፴ወ፱ዘመነ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለንጉሥነ፡ ኃይለ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ሥላሴ፡</hi> በእደ፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ አለቃ፡ ድራር፡ ወልደ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ ዘብሔረ፡
                                                         ልጋት፡ ወዘአጽሐፈቶ፡ ወይዘሮ፡ ምሕረታ፡ ወልደ፡ ኪዳን፡ በ፻ወ፳ብሩር፡ ወወሀበቶ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ዮሐንሰ፡ ደብረ፡ ማዕጾ፨ ዘሠረቆ፡
                                                         ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ርጉመ፡ ይኩን፡ ከመ፡ አርዮስ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን፨ 

                                                         <foreign xml:lang="en">This book was completed on
                                                           <date>2 Ṗagumen, in the year of mercy 1962</date>, in the 39th year of the reign of our king <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5226haylase">Ḫāyla Śǝllāse</persName>, by
                                                           the hands of the scribe <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13233DerarWaldaQirqos">ʾalaqā Dǝrār Walda Qirqos</persName>
                                                            of the country of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC7348Legat">Lǝgāt</placeName>. And
                                                         the one who caused him to write is <persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13234MehrataWaldaKidan">wayzāro Mǝḥratā Walda Kidān</persName>,
                                                         for 120 <foreign xml:lang="gez">Bǝrur</foreign>, and
                                                             she gave it to the <foreign xml:lang="gez">tābot</foreign> of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2320DabraM">Yoḥannǝs of Dabra Māʿṣo</placeName>. Anyone who stole it, or
                                                             who erased it, be cursed like Arius by authority of Peter and Paul. So be it,
                                                           so be it, so be it.</foreign></colophon>
